title: (Almost) Complete Ghostbusters Comic Collection [June 2014]
description:
All of the Ghostbusters comics spanning 25 years. Everything starting from NOW comics to the latest issue from IDW is in this torrent. Only 4 issues are missing:



(NOW Comics) Slimer! 11,16,19

(IDW) Ghostbusters: Haunted Holidays (new bonus story called Guess What's Coming to Dinner?)



If anyone has these please share and make this collection truly complete.


Enjoy Fans!
